vibesExplanation:
The workout exhibits qualities of 'The Endorphin Wave,' suggested by the continuous, steady resistance changes that build intensity over 25 minutes. The full-body engagement and energizing nature of elliptical workouts align with this vibe, especially given user comments describing feelings of exhilaration and motivation. This is supported by YouTube comments mentioning users feeling "energized and exhilarating" and more exhilarated than usual.

'"The Meditative Grind'" is also applicable due to the workout's repetitive nature and focus on endurance across different resistance levels. The session appears to be rhythmically structured with resistance changes and is meant to engage users in a steady, sustainable energy output, which fits the zone-in quality of this vibe. 

Lastly, '"The Progression Quest'" is present in the mentions of the intermediate level and users expressing their progression to higher resistance levels, thus emphasizing long-term improvement, even if it's not the primary focus. The scoring reflects a moderate resonance with this vibe.
